5️⃣ ORM (Hibernate) — VERY IMPORTANT

ORM = Object Relational Mapping.

It converts:

Java Object ↔ Database Table

Example:

Database:

users
id | name | email



Java:
@Entity
public class User {

    @Id
    private Long id;

    private String name;
    private String email;
}

Hibernate automatically:
	•	Converts object to SQL INSERT
	•	Converts DB row to Java object

You don’t write raw SQL most of the time.

That’s enough for now.
